    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Honest, affordable transportation with plenty of life left for the right buyer. This vehicle shows its age, but it remains a practical option for someone seeking a low-cost daily driver, backup car, or weekend project. A straightforward value buy with a price that reflects condition and leaves room in the budget for personal touches or future upkeep.",
