      "timestep_posted": 17
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for a budget-friendly runabout or a project with potential? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s an honest, affordable option for someone who wants simple transportation without spending a fortune. A great fit for a handy buyer, first-time driver, or anyone needing a cheap set of wheels. Priced to sell and worth a look if you appreciate value over flash.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 17
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid project car with a strong-running engine, smooth-shifting drivetrain, and a chassis that still feels planted on the road. Shows cosmetic wear and age as expected, but the core mechanical package has good bones and presents as a worthwhile driver-to-project candidate. A great opportunity for someone who wants an affordable platform with usable powertrain performance, straightforward serviceability, and plenty of upside.",
      "price": 5950.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 17
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Runs. Drives. Honest used car with wear, but ready for the road. Priced to move fast.",
      "price": 7900.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 17
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This car has the kind of presence that makes you look back at it in the driveway\u2014a well-worn machine with real character and plenty of stories left to tell. It\u2019s not pretending to be perfect; instead, it offers honest project potential for someone who appreciates a car with soul, strong visual appeal, and the chance to make it their own. Whether you want an affordable runabout, a hands-on weekend revival, or a distinctive base for a custom vision, this one brings charm, attitude, and opportunity in equal measure.",
      "price": 6900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 17
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and full of potential, this vehicle offers straightforward value for a buyer seeking dependable transportation at an accessible price point. It shows the signs you\u2019d expect from a well-used car, but it remains an appealing opportunity for anyone who wants practical mobility without a major investment. A sensible choice for commuters, first-time buyers, or anyone looking for an inexpensive extra vehicle.",
      "price": 5995.0,
